  <brief_title>Closed Loop Ventilation Strategy in Intensive Care Unit (ICU) Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of a Closed Loop Ventilation Strategy on Reducing the Total Duration of Mechanical Ventilation of Intubated Intensive Care Unit Patients: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
